OL,3,CMeet the high-tech drones looking to
OL,4,Cimprove water company leaks
OL,6,FWater company Severn Trent has
OL,7,Fembraced the latest technology to
OL,8,Fimprove its network - drones to spot
OL,9,Fleaks in its piping system.
OL,11,FBosses says the drones have saved the
OL,12,Fcompany "potentially hundreds of
OL,13,Fthousands" of pounds per year.
OL,15,FJonny Bevan, Drone Safety Officer said
OL,16,Fhe believes the drones will help the
OL,17,Fcompany maintain areas of its network
OL,18,Fthat are hard to access.
