OL,3,CMeet the high-tech drones looking to
OL,4,Cimprove water company leaks
OL,6,FJonny said: "We've got lots of fields,
OL,7,Flots of rural areas - using the drone
OL,8,Fwe can suddenly cover fast amounts of
OL,9,Fareas that you just wouldn't cover
OL,10,Fwith a person."
OL,12,FThe drones work by picking up leaks
OL,13,Fthrough thermal imaging - the imaging
OL,14,Fdetects water leaking out at a
OL,15,Fdifferent temperature from the
OL,16,Fsurrounding ground.
