OL,3,CMeet the high-tech drones looking to
OL,4,Cimprove water company leaks
OL,6,FBut any money saved by Severn Trent
OL,7,Fdrone technology will not pass on to
OL,8,Fcustomer bills. Severn Trent want to
OL,9,Fincrease customer's bills by 46% over
OL,10,Fthe next five years - money the
OL,11,Fcompany says will be spent on
OL,12,Fupgrading pipes, drains and sewers.
OL,14,FWatch one of Severn Trent's new drones
OL,15,Fexplore a pipe in the company's water
OL,16,Fnetwork, checking it for leaks.
