OL,3,CMeet the high-tech drones looking to
OL,4,Cimprove water company leaks
OL,6,FDuncan Turner, drone lead, said such
OL,7,F3D imaging "allows us to explore that
OL,8,Finternal space (of the tunnel). As the
OL,9,Fdrone goes through it maps it out and
OL,10,Fany photographs that we take it shows
OL,11,Fus exactly where on the model it has
OL,12,Ftaken them."
OL,14,FThe company has plans for unmanned
OL,15,Fpatrol drones - "Drone in a Box."
OL,16,FThese are drones that will live in a
OL,17,Fcage in remote areas, doing regular
OL,18,Fpatrols along critical pipe work, and
OL,19,Fcan be operated remotely.
